    <title>Saving your document</title>
    <shortdesc>CWRC-Writer allows you to save documents you have created on our server as temporary
        test files to work with. At the moment, however, we do not have individual authentication
        setup for each user, so it's best if you do not play with each other's files: this way each
        tester can have his/her own files to alter, add to, and so forth.</shortdesc>
